Global SOAR Tools and Solutions Market Insights
SOAR Tools and Solutions Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.6% from 2024 to 2030.

SOAR Tools and Solutions Market Overview
The Security Orchestration, Automation, and Response (SOAR) market is projected to grow from an estimated USD 1.1 billion in 2022 to USD 2.3 billion by 2027, reflecting a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of 15.8% during this period. This growth is driven by the increasing frequency of phishing emails and ransomware attacks, which SOAR solutions effectively mitigate by automating and streamlining security operations. Additionally, SOAR tools help alleviate alert fatigue among security teams, enhancing their efficiency and response times.

